
This example shows some ways of detctor simulation with using magnetic field.

1)   Global, uniform, and transverse magnetic field can be 
     applied using G4GlobalMagFieldMessenger, instantiated in 
     DetectorConstruction.cc with a non zero field value,
     or via interactive command:
     
     /globalField/setValue 0.2 0 0 tesla

2)   Global and local uniform and transverse (along X) magnetic field can be 
     applied using FieldSetup(), instantiated in 
     DetectorConstruction.cc 
     or via interactive command:
     
     /fild/setFieldX 0.2 0 0 tesla

